        "# Learning How to Translate\n",
        "\n",
        "## Translating PIE\n",
        "\n",
        "> H₂aláh₂. H₁nómn̥ moy H₁inigṓ montóyah₂ h₁esti. Gʷʰégʷʰens pəh₂térm̥ méne. Pékʷeswe mr̥téyey.\n",
        "\n",
        "### How on earth can be begin to translate this?\n",
        "\n",
        "## Steps to Translate\n",
        "\n",
        "1)  identify **verbs**\\\n",
        "2)  identify **subjects/objects** via case\\\n",
        "3)  find **other nominals** and words to complete your translation\\\n",
        "4)  shuffle word order to make it more English-like\n",
        "\n",
        "## Immersive PIE Text: together\n",
        "\n",
        "1.  H₁ésti h₁ógʷʰis. Só h₂wésti dʰəĝʰmí.\n",
        "\n",
        "2.  H₁ésti gʷṓws. Sáh₂ h₂wésti dʰəĝʰmí.\n",
        "\n",
        "3.  H₁ésti h₂ówis. Sáh₂ h₂wésti dʰəĝʰmí.\n",
        "\n",
        "4.  H₁ésti h₂áwis. H₁ésti trózdos. Só h₂wésti drḗw.\n",
        "\n",
        "5.  H₁ésti h₂áwis. H₁ésti k̂órh₂s. Só h₂wésti drḗw.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Immersive PIE Text: in groups\n",
